Comment: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將巨人...
Comment: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給殺死...
Comment: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一隻不留地...
Comment: 0,0:10:57.52,0:10:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個是!
Comment: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,住手!
Comment: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在還不清楚艾連能不能分辨出妳是誰
Comment: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那傢伙...
Comment: 0,0:11:56.01,0:11:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,想要爬上...
Comment: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,牆壁是嗎?!
Comment: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不行了!
Comment: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣下去要讓她逃走了!
Comment: 0,0:12:16.16,0:12:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,休想得逞!
Comment: 0,0:12:32.97,0:12:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮...
Comment: 0,0:12:35.99,0:12:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,下去吧
Comment: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮...
Comment: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是我錯了...
Comment: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,事到如今我已不再奢求妳的原諒
Comment: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是...
Comment: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只有一件事...
Comment: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我想拜託妳...
Comment: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,即便跟這世上的一切為敵也沒關係
Comment: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我要...
Comment: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將這世上全部的東西都給...
Comment: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,破壞殆盡!
Comment: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就算妳被整個世界...
Comment: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給怨恨著...
Comment: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只有爸爸...
Comment: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,永遠是妳的夥伴
Comment: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,慘了!
Comment: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣裡面也要被吃掉了!
Comment: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連住手啊!
Comment: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我是...
Comment: 0,0:13:35.01,0:13:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,自由的!
Comment: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以請妳答應我...
Comment: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要平安回來...
Comment: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,發生什麼事了?
Comment: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼了?
Comment: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,融化了!?
Comment: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎能把重要的證人給吃了
Comment: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,白癡
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,CM
Comment: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮呢...
Comment: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可惡...
Comment: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,到底是怎樣啦!
Comment: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,都到這一步了 還什麼都不說嗎!
Comment: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮!
Comment: 0,0:15:45.66,0:15:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我出來!
Comment: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,出來把事情做個了斷啊!
Comment: 0,0:15:49.35,0:15:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂!太卑鄙了喔!
Comment: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮!
Comment: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮!!
Comment: 0,0:15:55.38,0:15:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,住手
Comment: 0,0:15:58.36,0:15:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒用的
Comment: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,用繩索編個網子
Comment: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,把這個綑起來送到地下去
Comment: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,了解
Comment: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就一直這樣...
Comment: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,都沒從亞妮身上得到任何情報的話...
Comment: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那還剩下什麼...?
Comment: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,犧牲了這麼多人...
Comment: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,毀了他們的人生...
Comment: 0,0:16:22.09,0:16:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,卻只留下一堆謎團...
Comment: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,又能怎麼樣呢...
Comment: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,說不上是作戰成功呢
Comment: 0,0:16:40.63,0:16:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不
Comment: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們調查軍團的脖子已經接上了
Comment: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,恐怕只是脖子上的一片小皮而已
Comment: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果是這樣就好了
Comment: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾爾文
Comment: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,關於這次的作戰有幾個問題要問你
Comment: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,既然已經知道目標是誰了
Comment: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼沒有找憲兵團來幫忙?
Comment: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,區長
Comment: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那是因為只要是女巨人的夥伴可能埋伏在附近的話
Comment: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們就必須用能夠證明自己是清白的人來執行任務
Comment: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是
Comment: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為這樣史托黑斯區所受到的損害又要怎麼辦?
Comment: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是我們實力不足所造成的
Comment: 0,0:17:30.83,0:17:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我為我的粗心謝罪
Comment: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是道歉就能解決的事情嗎!
Comment: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果讓她繼續這樣下去的話
Comment: 0,0:17:36.79,0:17:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,牆壁會被破壞
Comment: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,損害肯定會比現在還嚴重
Comment: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,原來如此
Comment: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,關於這次付出了巨大的損失的作戰
Comment: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有得到能阻止人類的滅亡的確切證據嗎?
Comment: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我是不覺得能從亞妮雷恩哈特身上得到
Comment: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是的 應該是不可能了
Comment: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也就是說...
Comment: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,完全是白白犧牲了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:18:19.31,0:18:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,身體還好嗎?
Comment: 0,0:18:23.06,0:18:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯
Comment: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不舒服的感覺還是跟原本一樣
Comment: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮她...
Comment: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還是一樣硬化著呢
Comment: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯
Comment: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,該死...
Comment: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,用了那麼大規模的作戰 結果卻連一點收穫都沒有嗎!
Comment: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也就是亞妮她守護情報到那種程度了
Comment: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯 被她順利地逃掉了
Comment: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,讓她逃掉的是艾連
Comment: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒錯吧 艾連
Comment: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果沒有那一瞬間的話
Comment: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是啊
Comment: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就跟阿爾敏說的一樣
Comment: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我失手了
Comment: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,看到亞妮之後
Comment: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我就下不了手了
Comment: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏．亞魯雷特
Comment: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,約翰．基爾休坦
Comment: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要來盤問事由了
Comment: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好的
Comment: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從我們兩個開始嗎?
Comment: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那就...回頭見
Comment: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個時候...
Comment: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我覺得很舒服
Comment: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,身體快壞掉了還覺得很清爽
Comment: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,覺得既然如此 就這樣...
Comment: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,死了也沒關係
Comment: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在沒那樣想了啦
Comment: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你活著回來...
Comment: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真是太好了
Comment: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我沒辦法理解呢
Comment: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果要超越怪物的話
Comment: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就必須連人性也捨棄掉...
Comment: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不這樣的話贏不了嗎...
Comment: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是人類要贏過巨人的可能性之一
Comment: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我認為艾連做得到
Comment: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我說...即使變成那種怪物把巨人驅逐掉了...
Comment: 0,0:20:43.52,0:20:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那還算是人類的勝利嗎?
Comment: 0,0:20:56.86,0:20:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,吃吧
Comment: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒辦法...簡單地就超越...
Comment: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是
Comment: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我認為我抓住了讓人類生存下去的...
Comment: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,巨大的可能性
Comment: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是還沒思考過人類能巨人化
Comment: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,抓住敵人的其中一人  是很大的進步
Comment: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒錯
Comment: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那些傢伙一定還在
Comment: 0,0:21:43.93,0:21:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,讓我們把他們逼進絕路吧
Comment: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將那些在牆壁內的巨人們
Comment: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一個不剩地
Comment: 0,0:21:51.47,0:21:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這次該是我們進擊的時候了!
Comment: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,調查軍團與艾連．葉卡召回王都的命令被凍結
Comment: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,被收在地下深處的亞妮．雷恩哈特的管理
Comment: 0,0:22:08.88,0:22:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,被交由調查軍團來負責
Comment: 0,0:22:12.58,0:22:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然而
Comment: 0,0:22:14.25,0:22:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類要知道自己被什麼東西給囚禁著的話
Comment: 0,0:22:20.98,0:22:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還需要更多的時間與犧牲
