Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:50.88,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\fsp5\bord2\blur5\c&HCDCDCD&\pos(977.015,735.766)}─史托黑斯區突襲③─
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.57,0:00:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.96,0:00:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這世界就是如此殘酷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.13,0:00:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我要...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.75,0:00:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}驅逐你們...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是殺光你們!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類回想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在他們支配之下的恐懼...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}以及被囚禁在鳥籠之中的...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}屈辱...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.01,0:00:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}讓我們來祈禱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}羅塞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}席納
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:02:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}祈求三位女神依然健在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.58,0:03:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}祈禱大家的平安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}神聖的城牆不容許任何的質疑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}神之手親自打造的三道城牆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是因為我們的信仰之心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}才變得更加堅固
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}相信神明的純潔之心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}才是保護我們免於巨人危害的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.19,0:03:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也是唯一能擊退巨人的力量...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼會在這裡!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.89,0:03:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不可以...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不可以接近城牆...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}接近城牆...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這次似乎也保持住自己的意識了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.72,0:04:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.83,0:04:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連到目前為止一次也沒有贏過女巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他變成巨人了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他應該肚子非常餓的才對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:31.63,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}應該不會這麼簡單就...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}戰鬥... 並不是靠氣勢就能贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}約翰你應該也知道才對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要打倒那個亞妮...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.25,0:04:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要更加地...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是平地!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}女巨人要進入平地了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到那邊的話就無法進行立體機動!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}全部的人都向後撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}了解!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點 快點 快點啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}太奇怪了吧 為什麼巨人會...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳總是擺著一副大家都是白癡的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總是一臉感到很無趣的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但妳還是有充滿活力的時候...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就是妳在施展格鬥術的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然妳說學格鬥術一點意義都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但對我來說...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不認為妳心中是那麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳是個...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}很不會說謊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我一直以來都是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我說 亞妮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為了什麼而戰?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是因為什麼大義
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}才去殺人的!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}分隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算成功捕捉到女巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.51,0:06:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣下去城鎮會變成廢墟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}即便如此還是要做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是艾爾文下的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你也去做好捕捉的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我可沒聽過有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼這裡會有巨人在戰鬥?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到底...怎麼了...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你說巨人在互相戰鬥?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}城鎮損害到無法想像的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}居民與士兵出現了很多死傷者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾爾文!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這全部都是你的作戰所引發的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}全部都是我獨斷的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我沒打算狡辯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果在城鎮中實施這樣的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你應該知道事態會變成怎樣才是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼 你還能幹得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為了人類的...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你開什麼玩笑!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你這個反叛者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算我在此把你處刑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}想必上頭也不會說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒差
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}剩下來的指揮就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}蛤?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}絕對不要讓女巨人逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}隊伍展開是由佩魯擔當
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}補給是由拜依拉擔當
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}先去跟他們會合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再去東邊牆邊將女巨人給...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:12.72,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.06,0:08:13.59,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:14.56,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等等!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個...真的...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是為了人類才...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我相信這會成為那一大步
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}全部的人把槍放下!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給他們上手銬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將所有的士兵全部派去現場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}優先完成居民的避難以及救援
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.59,0:08:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是的!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.31,0:08:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾爾文
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你的處刑就用正當的懲罰來解決
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等全部結束後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我很樂意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}里維
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你別行動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你很討厭送死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是啊 很討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}無論是去死還是讓人去死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}無法捨去任何東西的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就無法改變任何東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果需要凌駕怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.21,0:09:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就連人性也可捨去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.99,0:09:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我想亞妮她...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.28,0:09:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就是做得到這點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只有爸爸...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}才是妳的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我要...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將巨人...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給殺死...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一隻不留地...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:10:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個是!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在還不清楚艾連能不能分辨出妳是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那傢伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.01,0:11:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}想要爬上...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}牆壁是嗎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不行了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣下去要讓她逃走了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.16,0:12:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}休想得逞!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.97,0:12:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.99,0:12:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是我錯了...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}事到如今我已不再奢求妳的原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只有一件事...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我想拜託妳...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}即便跟這世上的一切為敵也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我要...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將這世上全部的東西都給...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}破壞殆盡!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算妳被整個世界...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給怨恨著...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只有爸爸...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}永遠是妳的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}慘了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣裡面也要被吃掉了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連住手啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.01,0:13:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}自由的!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以請妳答應我...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要平安回來...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}發生什麼事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}融化了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎能把重要的證人給吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到底是怎樣啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}都到這一步了 還什麼都不說嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.66,0:15:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我出來!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}出來把事情做個了斷啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.35,0:15:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂!太卑鄙了喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.38,0:15:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.36,0:15:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}用繩索編個網子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}把這個綑起來送到地下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就一直這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}都沒從亞妮身上得到任何情報的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那還剩下什麼...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}犧牲了這麼多人...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}毀了他們的人生...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.09,0:16:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}卻只留下一堆謎團...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}又能怎麼樣呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}說不上是作戰成功呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.63,0:16:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們調查軍團的脖子已經接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}恐怕只是脖子上的一片小皮而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果是這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾爾文
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}關於這次的作戰有幾個問題要問你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}既然已經知道目標是誰了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼沒有找憲兵團來幫忙?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}區長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那是因為只要是女巨人的夥伴可能埋伏在附近的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們就必須用能夠證明自己是清白的人來執行任務
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為這樣史托黑斯區所受到的損害又要怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是我們實力不足所造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.83,0:17:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我為我的粗心謝罪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是道歉就能解決的事情嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果讓她繼續這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.79,0:17:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}牆壁會被破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}損害肯定會比現在還嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}關於這次付出了巨大的損失的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有得到能阻止人類的滅亡的確切證據嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我是不覺得能從亞妮雷恩哈特身上得到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是的 應該是不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也就是說...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}完全是白白犧牲了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.31,0:18:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}身體還好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.06,0:18:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不舒服的感覺還是跟原本一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮她...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還是一樣硬化著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}該死...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}用了那麼大規模的作戰 結果卻連一點收穫都沒有嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也就是亞妮她守護情報到那種程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}嗯 被她順利地逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}讓她逃掉的是艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒錯吧 艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果沒有那一瞬間的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就跟阿爾敏說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我失手了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}看到亞妮之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我就下不了手了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏．亞魯雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}約翰．基爾休坦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要來盤問事由了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從我們兩個開始嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那就...回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個時候...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我覺得很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}身體快壞掉了還覺得很清爽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}覺得既然如此 就這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}死了也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在沒那樣想了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你活著回來...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我沒辦法理解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果要超越怪物的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就必須連人性也捨棄掉...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不這樣的話贏不了嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是人類要贏過巨人的可能性之一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我認為艾連做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我說...即使變成那種怪物把巨人驅逐掉了...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.52,0:20:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那還算是人類的勝利嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:20:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒辦法...簡單地就超越...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我認為我抓住了讓人類生存下去的...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨大的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是還沒思考過人類能巨人化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}抓住敵人的其中一人  是很大的進步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那些傢伙一定還在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.93,0:21:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}讓我們把他們逼進絕路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將那些在牆壁內的巨人們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一個不剩地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.47,0:21:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這次該是我們進擊的時候了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}調查軍團與艾連．葉卡召回王都的命令被凍結
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}被收在地下深處的亞妮．雷恩哈特的管理
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.88,0:22:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}被交由調查軍團來負責
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.58,0:22:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}然而
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.25,0:22:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類要知道自己被什麼東西給囚禁著的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.98,0:22:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還需要更多的時間與犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.96,0:22:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}
